videos.description: Arkansas State's Ty Cockfield makes a tough 3-pointer to keep the game close vs. Syracuse.
videos.headline: Arkansas St guard buries tough 3

videos.description: Oshae Brissett finds Elijah Hughes on a nice cut to set up a layup  and an and-1.
